  "texts": [
    "Subsequently we identified SV using Sniffles2 with both germline (default) and mosaic mode.",
    "The Bionano OGM data smap file was converted by SURVIVOR smaptovcf (version 1.0.7) into a VCF file.",
    "To compare SVs called by Sniffles2, Manta (Illumina) and OGM (Bionano), we used SURVIVOR merge using a 10-kb threshold, matching SV type and ignoring reported SV strand.",
    "We extended it to 10 kbp after testing 500 1-kbp and 5-kbp thresholds and observed that the accuracy of the breakpoints from OGM required the larger parameter.",
    "The genotype columns in the SURVIVOR merge output were compared for each SV to determine presence or absence in the results reported by the respective method."
  ],
